basIfMIB.name: basIfMIB
basIfMIB.contactinfo: Tech Support Broadband Access Systems, Inc. 201 Forest Street Marlborough, MA 01752 USA 508-485-8200 support@basystems.com
basIfMIB.description: The MIB module defines the configuration MIB objects for Broadband Access Systems, Inc. interfaces extensions.

basIfTable.name: basIfTable
basIfTable.description: A list of interface entries. The number of entries is given by the value of ifNumber.

basIfEntry.name: basIfEntry
basIfEntry.description: An entry containing management information applicable to a particular interface.

basIfChassis.name: basIfChassis
basIfChassis.description: The BAS Chassis ID of this card.

basIfSlot.name: basIfSlot
basIfSlot.description: The BAS Slot ID of this card.

basIfInterface.name: basIfInterface
basIfInterface.description: The BAS interface ID of this card.

basIfLPort.name: basIfLPort
basIfLPort.description: The BAS logical port ID of this card.

basIfClass.name: basIfClass
basIfClass.description: The BAS class of this interface.

basIfSimpleProxyArp.name: basIfSimpleProxyArp
basIfSimpleProxyArp.description: Enable or disable simple proxy ARP so CMTS hosts can communicate with one another.

basIfDhcpCmSubnet.name: basIfDhcpCmSubnet
basIfDhcpCmSubnet.description: Subnet to use for giaddr for cable modem DHCP requests.

basIfDhcpHostSubnet.name: basIfDhcpHostSubnet
basIfDhcpHostSubnet.description: Subnet to use for giaddr for host DHCP requests.

basIfArpAgingDisable.name: basIfArpAgingDisable
basIfArpAgingDisable.description: Enable or disable timing out ARP enties on this interface.

basIfSecurityFilter.name: basIfSecurityFilter
basIfSecurityFilter.description: Enable or disable security filtering on this interface. If this filter is enabled all packets sent to 10.x.13.x from a CM other than SNMP,DHCP,ICMP,TOD,SYSLOG, and TFTP will be dropped and all packets from CPE other than ICMP and DHCP will be dropped.
